{"tid":205845,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"台灣保存「最好的中國」   台北故宮博物館,  香港粵英文化望塵莫及！","createTime":"2017-04-18T05:32:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-19T14:13:43.000Z","uid":79563,"like":5,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a9208e883534c9a5a9a18558adf1a67a3e419a48","tid":205845,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T05:32:02.000Z","msg":"香港係粵英文化<br />\n<br />\n「保存最好的中國」係台灣！<br />\n<br />\n 台北故宮博物館有更多「中國」文化收藏品！<br />\n<br />\n絕對比香港更「中國」！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.npm.gov.tw/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.npm.gov.tw%2F&d=TNVh%2FXBsTmD9bRjMILuVa%2BPnIAwyWqphGIcg0J4V%2Buw%3D&h=5c4cd5ef\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.npm.gov.tw/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://mays2.weebly.com/uploads/5/6/7/6/5676424/9630866_orig.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmays2.weebly.com%2Fuploads%2F5%2F6%2F7%2F6%2F5676424%2F9630866_orig.jpg&h=1d64bf2a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"728618480cffdd4cc878b31029a41f4fd94df5c1","tid":205845,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T05:32:58.000Z","msg":"台灣認「中國」, 真係實至名歸！<br />\n<br />\n香港半桶水, 真係無可能同台北故宮博物館爭！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd9e980f02ca1a926751a06d424b5edd2f8b307f","tid":205845,"uid":498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T05:37:32.000Z","msg":"故宮正門入定樓梯攻上去"},{"pid":"22535b80efaa77de2be0c7fc23c1f201c8131f33","tid":205845,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T05:43:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>故宮正門入定樓梯攻上去</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n空降都得, 你鍾意啦！"},{"pid":"298eb674bb7bbf0df0a54079bb1cc77cd3757bbf","tid":205845,"uid":44454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T05:50:50.000Z","msg":"呢樣我真係認輸啦，好爭唔爭鬥中國化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8709223998badbc3b3a7c62055bcf241d76cd880","tid":205845,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T05:51:54.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">台北故宮博物館鎮館之寶 ─ 毛公鼎！</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n你班港豬同台灣鬥「中國」？ 真係不知天高地厚！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.npm.gov.tw/exh99/bell/images/index_r11_c1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.npm.gov.tw%2Fexh99%2Fbell%2Fimages%2Findex_r11_c1.jpg&h=a947fe0d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n毛公鼎高53.8厘米，口徑47.9厘米，是據今2800多年前週宣王時期的&ldquo;國之重<br />\n <br />\n器&rdquo;，因刻器者為毛公而得名，於清道光末年在陝西岐山出土<br />\n <br />\n。 在中國，有兩件青銅器堪稱青銅器之最，一件是保存在北京國家博物館的司母戊大方鼎，它<br />\n <br />\n是迄今為止發現的最大最重的青銅器，<br />\n <br />\n另一件就是銘文最多的這件毛公鼎。<br />\n <br />\n毛公鼎是一件宗廟祭器，它的內壁鑄有五百個字的長銘，是現存商週兩代七千<br />\n <br />\n多件有銘文的銅器中，銘文最長的一件。<br />\n <br />\n銘文的內容可分成七段，大意是說：週宣王即位之初，亟思振興<br />\n <br />\n朝政，乃請叔父毛公為其治理國家內外的大小政務，並飭勤公無私，又令毛公<br />\n <br />\n族人擔任禁衛軍，保護王室，最後頒贈厚賜，<br />\n <br />\n毛公因而鑄鼎傳示子孫永寶，由內容推測，毛公鼎應鑄於週<br />\n <br />\n宣王元年（公元前827年）時，其銘文是可凌駕於〔尚書〕的一篇西周真實史<br />\n <br />\n料，是研究西周史最珍貴的文獻，<br />\n <br />\n也因此毛公鼎可稱是舉世的瑰寶重器。<br />\n   <br />\n 毛公鼎出土後，經多次轉手秘藏，抗戰期間，險為日本軍方所奪，抗戰勝利，<br />\n <br />\n民間獻鼎歸公。銘文中有陽文網格線，<br />\n <br />\n是西周中晚期制銘的習慣，因此除了史料的價值外，毛公鼎在中<br />\n <br />\n國古文字學與書法藝術上也具有舉足輕重的地位。"},{"pid":"c052219016cbcec462ea577bfbb9dda089878a2d","tid":205845,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T05:53:47.000Z","msg":"港大歷史系 Professor Carroll, John M.<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s15.postimg.org/tofgq13xn/AAA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs15.postimg.org%2Ftofgq13xn%2FAAA.jpg&h=06a05559&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n同台灣鬥「中國」？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66068e0c6272737eeba269f66e9da195634e375b","tid":205845,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T05:54:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢樣我真係認輸啦，好爭唔爭鬥中國化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有班青山大中華膠, 話要同台灣鬥「中國」喎！<br />\n<br />\n真係人唔笑, 狗都吠啦！"},{"pid":"fe8fcb2b70b3f3b08e23029af58c05a27028834a","tid":205845,"uid":23445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T06:03:11.000Z","msg":"個個外國朋友去完台灣屌晒老母<br />\n話台北故宮博物館冇野睇,得啖笑"},{"pid":"f919311981a5809bb98bfceabc700f247e815554","tid":205845,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T06:04:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個個外國朋友去完台灣屌晒老母<br />\n話台北故宮博物館冇野睇,得啖笑</blockquote><br />\n根本得幾件比較珍貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1fab7d9850763e816a25e1348e77ea158c25f9a","tid":205845,"uid":60015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T06:05:30.000Z","msg":"得罪講句故宮博物館個設計真係好柒<br />\n入撚過去一次<br />\n好撚垃圾<br />\n柒過日本是但一間藝術館"},{"pid":"0ed2865154f67eec91c8bbe675c9733a2a035031","tid":205845,"uid":8543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T06:06:18.000Z","msg":"正統中國送都唔要"},{"pid":"6f5a10fd1ea76bdfb49e3b1e4e6d7b1790f6d1ef","tid":205845,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T06:07:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>正統中國送都唔要</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咪係, 台仔咁鍾意, 拿去用啦！<br />\n<br />\n好行夾唔送！"},{"pid":"802890062aa7b22f009d710100dd84a8eb962b17","tid":205845,"uid":39733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T06:09:00.000Z","msg":"邊撚個咁 on9 要同兩個中國鬥「中國」？<br />\n貪「中國」個名夠馨香咩"},{"pid":"df67aeea949b4a349f0d03e806a5e2fc0db208ee","tid":205845,"uid":67302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T06:10:49.000Z","msg":"on9 搵鬼要中國個朵咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 